      "At line 192 the contract approves `attackerEOA` for `campaign.amount`.",
      "The attacker calls the token contract's `transferFrom(address(ClaimCampaigns), attackerEOA, amount)` and drains the shared escrow.",
      "If a campaign is later cancelled, line 256 returns only `campaign.amount` but does not clear prior approval, so the approved locker can drain later deposits of the same token as well."
    ]
